# Naninovel
# https://github.com/ja67/NaninovelIntegrationExample/blob/master/.gitignore
/Assets/ThirdParty/Naninovel*
/Assets/NaninovelData/Saves*

# https://discord.com/channels/545676116871086080/557519193520603136/1339969117054042252
# Also you don't have to ignore Metadata and ProjectStats. They may be useful. It's just we don't need them in samples. hence they're ignored.
# But yeah, that's a matter of preference.
# Bridging and Saves are the only ones that have to be always ignored. Will add that to the docs.
/Assets/NaninovelData/.nani/Bridging*
/Assets/NaninovelData/Saves*

# 1.2.0版本實際安裝的路徑
/Assets/NaninovelData/.nani/Transient/Bridging
/Assets/NaninovelData/.nani/Transient/Saves

# Addressables相關的路徑
/DisabledImporterBuildPath
/ServerData

# 打包 Android 平台時出現，可能是 CMake 的資料夾
.utmp

# 忽略所有 Excel 的暫存檔
~$*

# 忽略所有 Asset Hunter PRO 插件在打包版本後產生的檔案
SerializedBuildInfo

# 忽略 UnityEditorGitTool 插件儲存的檔案
Assets/Resources/GitHash.asset
Assets/Resources/GitHash.asset.meta
Assets/_AX/Scripts/NakamaClient/Resources/Configs/NakamaConfig.asset

# 本地/暫存 UI 素材, 不納入版控
Assets/_AX/Art/Sprite/Preview
Assets/_AX/Art/Sprite/Preview.meta
Assets/_AX/Art/Sprite/UIElement/_PlainBoard
Assets/_AX/Art/Sprite/UIElement/_PlainBoard.meta
